{"tid":749453,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"網曝《EVA》新劇場版2020年上映  預告來的太意外","createTime":"2018-07-20T04:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T09:59:49.000Z","uid":49391,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"38dcc74c3bf611f156f736fc69a7f9d117e25220","tid":749453,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"今天（7月20日）是動畫導演細田守新作《未來的未來》上映的日子，在twitter上，一些自稱前去觀影的用戶表示，在《未來的未來》貼片特報中公開了《 EVA》新劇場版的新預告，同時宣布這部《EVA》劇場版將在2020年上映！我們目前暫時還無法確認事情的真實性，且暫時還沒有影片內容髮布，大家也請謹慎看待。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180720_lr_176_3/gamersky_01small_02_20187201059666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180720_lr_176_3%2Fgamersky_01small_02_20187201059666.jpg&h=50d4e0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180720_lr_176_3/gamersky_02small_04_20187201059BF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180720_lr_176_3%2Fgamersky_02small_04_20187201059BF6.jpg&h=a1374df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前《EVA》新劇場版宣布開始製作，官方陸陸續續的公開了一些概念海報、角色動圖，基本上就是一直在強調動畫已經在做了。這次的預告完全沒有任何宣傳，而且先在劇場公開也是給了大家一個驚喜，感覺庵野秀明的套路真是猜不透，還是耐心的等著他們發布消息吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180720_lr_176_3/gamersky_03small_06_201872010592E1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180720_lr_176_3%2Fgamersky_03small_06_201872010592E1.jpg&h=8747c68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180720_lr_176_3/gamersky_04small_08_201872010596F6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180720_lr_176_3%2Fgamersky_04small_08_201872010596F6.jpg&h=7820f843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53ab9259108be4ec4630edf39b4cb43be560fa49","tid":749453,"uid":46933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cite